:Differing Deficiency
1-90,Identical to the Progenitor
91-100,[Gene Seed Deficiency]

:Gene Seed Deficiency
1,Hyper-stimulate Omophagea (Having tasted the flesh of the foe once, the Chapter's Battle Brothers develop an addiction tot he process allowed by the Omophagea.  When a brother is confronted with the opportunity to partake on the flesh of a fallen enemy must pass a Challenging (+0) Willpower Test or do so immediately, whether he wants to or not.)
2,Oversensitive Occulobe (The organ that allows Space marines to see in low light conditions has become overly sensitized, working extremely well in the dark but suffering in full light conditions.  The brother can see in total darkness as if it were merely low light, and low light as if it were full light.  However, should he remove his helmet in full light conditions he will suffer -10 to all Awareness Tests.)
3,Mutated Catalepsean Node (The implant that allows a Battle Brother to enter a half-sleep in which he can remain alert for danger has become dangerously mutated.  The Brother is unable to sleep normally, and stays awake for days, even weeks on end without effect.  However, when sleep does come, sometimes with little or no warning, it will last for many days on end.
4,Oolitic Secretions (The brother's oolitic kidney function is unbalanced in a way that the Battle Brother's skin is an unusual colour due to its secretions.
5,Disturbing Voice (Due to malfunction in or releated to the function of the Betcher's gland, the Chapter's brethren exhibit unusual focal characteristics.  Either not speaking abovie a sibilant whisper, or having deep booming voices, or speaking with an otherworldly cant.  Allies might find the effect disturbing, while enemies are likely to find it truly terrifying.  All Space Marines with this deficiency have the Disturbing Voice Talent.)
6-8,Lost(Missing or Inactive) Zygote(s) ([Missing or Inactive Zygote])
9,Doomed (Lost ability to replicate either the Black Carapace or Progenoid zygote.  Without future generations of Space Marines they will not be able to interface with their power armour (Black Carapace), and without the latter there will be no future generations at all (Progenoid zygote).  All brothers are unaffected themselves, but know that unless the Chapter's Apothecaries can affect a cure, they are the very last of their line.)
10,(Ignore Duplicates) {Loop~{Dice~1d3},[Gene Seed Deficiency2] }

